<P>A LETTER TO Mr. <HI>BISSET,</HI> Elde&s;t Brother of the Collegiate Church of St. <HI>Catherines;</HI> In ANSWER to his REMARKS ON <HI>Dr.</HI> SACHEVEREL'S <HI>Sermon.</HI></P>
